#Text=Fit in the Crowd With Being Who You Are
#Text=You know. .
#Text=Sometimes we 're wondering of what we 're going to do in the future .
#Text=We keep on wondering , until there 's a time where you feel lonely and your life is n't that fun .
#Text=Well , get up ! Keep on reading this to fit in the crowd without having to change your style or personality .
#Text=Only changing the way you treat people would make it .
#Text=Steps
#Text=Do n't be stubborn when people are telling good compliments about you .
#Text=This makes people think you 're overreacting .
#Text=Especially for girls .
#Text=What 's the hard thing of saying " Thank You " on every compliment that people are giving ?
#Text=" If there 's just one kind of folks , why ca n't they get along with each other ?
#Text=Be honest at every situation .
#Text=It 's the important thing to be honest to everyone you know .
#Text=Especially when an honesty action is needed , do n't hesitate to be honest .
#Text=Be fun !
#Text=Do n't be mad at every little jokes your friend made on you .
#Text=It 's just a joke and nothing is more .
#Text=If you 're being mad , than. . it means the joke is a fact of which involves you .
#Text=Unless if someone did a really annoying thing and really mean thing , you can do something .
#Text=Or , if you found those kinds of people , leave them alone and they 're gonna be shy themselves because of their joke are n't accepted by any deal .
#Text=Be nice to everyone ! People wo n't accept you if you 're perfect but mean !
#Text=when someone needs a help , give them one and do n't hesitate of giving your energy .
#Text=Be who you are .
#Text=You will fit in the crowd if you 're following the tips above .
#Text=But it does n't mean you 're gonna fit in the crowd happily .
#Text=The only thing to be happy is being who you are .
#Text=Tips
#Text=do n't change the way you walk , eat , talk or anything .
#Text=Just be who you are and everything will be just perfect .
#Text=Warnings
#Text=NEVER overreact !
#Text=Because that will only make people get annoyed .
